The summer is a perfection weather, because it is good for many things such as swimming, traveling and shopping. Personally I like this weather but my basic problem is the high temperatures that I can't do many things in high temperatures. Today the air conditioning invention come to solve this problem, that people can work in their office in a cold weather. Also they can do a shopping and drive the car and doing several things on the hot air because the air conditioner solve this problem. However it is a good solution but some researchers as Hedge and Gaygen claim that optimum work temperature is +23-24 Celsius and people are less productive and make more mistakes if the room temperature us lower than that, therefore there are an advantages for the air conditioner and it is considered a good solution for the higher temperatures. However, it has disadvantages also many researchers found that the air conditioner is the cause of spread diseases and his disadvantages is more than his advantages.